akn:section.akn:heading: Ownership by State of California of works constructed

akn:content.akn:p: § 695h. Ownership by State of California of works constructed Works constructed under the authorization of section 695e of this title, for the purpose of supplying State wildlife management areas with water, shall become the property of the State of California when constructed. (Aug. 27, 1954, ch. 1012, § 5, 68 Stat. 879.)
